			<div class="col-md-11 col-sm-11 col-xs-12 no-padding">
				<h1>11 things you can do to protect against ransomware, including Cryptolocker</h1>
<div class="excerpt">11 things you can be doing to better protect your computers and data from ransomware such as Cryptolocker that is currently targeting businesses big and small.</div>
<div class="post-meta">
    <div class="wls-authors">
